:::Wheeljack:::

Wheeljack: Yes, im sure i can.
::He goes to a computer::
Wheeljack: Computer scan Maximal City for energy signatures.
Computer: Scanning now.
::A few minutes later::
Computer: There are many energy signatures outside of Maximal City.  They are 
Maximal and Decepticon.
Wheeljack: Well, it seems that the Decepticons are trying their luck on the 
Maximals again.  Before we go any farther, I suggest we contact Zardus about 
this.
::He opens his comm::
Wheeljack: Commander Zardus, Vamprah and Composer are almost ready for their 
mission.  The only problem is that there is a battle going on at Maximal 
City.  We'd like to know what we should do.

OOC: Now we're stuck until Yan starts posting.

--part1_15b.164f74c.28deb434_boundary
